creator: Agens AS
descriptionHtml:
The app no knitter would want to be without!

Stay on top of all your knitting projects: those you might want to do, those in progress, and finished ones. With the KNIT app, you always have the information you need right at your needle tips: The pattern, which yarn you have used with color codes and batch numbers, sizes, needle types as well as your own notes and annotations.

Right now, we are working on several exciting new features:

— Yarn and needle inventory
— Customized and mobile-friendly knitting patterns, allowing you to set the size, and then only see relevant details (kiss parentheses goodbye!)
— Categorization of your recipes

We would love to hear your ideas on how we can make KNIT even better. Please reach out in the app.

title: KNIT

creator: Agens AS
descriptionHtml:
The app no knitter would want to be without!

Stay on top of all your knitting projects: those you might want to do, those in progress, and finished ones. With the KNIT app, you always have the information you need right at your needle tips: The pattern, which yarn you have used with color codes and batch numbers, sizes, needle types as well as your own notes and annotations.

Right now, we are working on several exciting new features:

— Yarn and needle inventory
— Customized and mobile-friendly knitting patterns, allowing you to set the size, and then only see relevant details (kiss parentheses goodbye!)
— Categorization of your recipes

We would love to hear your ideas on how we can make KNIT even better. Please reach out in the app.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We have made a new yarn schema for your projects for Christmas, so you can more easily add any new yarn you find under the tree 🎄 We have also upgraded the photo selector to a simpler and faster version for those of you on Android 10 and newer.
